         MetroStar Systems is looking for a Data SME that is passionate about architecting secure, reliable, highly-available data systems. If you want to join a company that values individuals with a strong systems background and a desire to securely design and implement new technologies for a large agency and are open to commuting to Reston, VA and with occasional travel to Charleston, SC, we want you to work for MetroStar!
